    <div class="main review-item" id="1158053">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1158053/" class="title-link">人生三境</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1158053"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1345469/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1345469-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1345469/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">sunny</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-05-20"
      class="main-meta">2007-05-20 12:07:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1158053_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  　　偶拾这本《且听人间词话》， 读毕，自己还陶醉在如此这般的意境中不能自拔。生活中的痛苦和酸涩是无法避免的，那我们还能做什么呢？只有做自己喜欢做的事情，去稀释这份苦涩。不知不觉地在此意境中安然平静得起真味．．．．．．  　　人的精神成长犹如一棵树，不到一定的年...

