  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8116510">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8116510/" class="title-link">人间词话记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8116510"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/134741708/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u134741708-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/134741708/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">明明如月</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-10-05"
      class="main-meta">2016-10-05 21:15:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8116510_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一、境界说 词以境界为最上。有境界自成高格，自有名句。五代北宋词所以独绝者在此。 （人间词话.壹） 有造景，有写境，此理想与写实二派之所由分。然二者颇难分别。因大诗人所造之境，必合乎自然，所写之境，亦必邻于理想故也。 （人间词话.贰） .......有我之境，以我观物，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
