  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4925833">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4925833/" class="title-link">吴淡如细腻而敏锐的评注，犹如讲故事般娓娓道来。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4925833"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/owenyao/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4457590-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/owenyao/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">豆芽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-28"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-28 15:04:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4925833_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  少了些学术味，多了些散文味。  每个为《人间词话》写评注的人，都会有自己的理解。正所谓“一千个读者就有一千个哈姆雷特”。吴的评注增添了很多女性的敏锐与细腻。  书的插图很漂亮。  而且把词话中涉及的诗词和作者的信息都列了出来，很方便阅读。附注还有静安未发表的手稿...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4925833_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4925833_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3517089">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3517089/" class="title-link">优美的其实还是词作本身</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3517089"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36154587/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36154587-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36154587/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">萨拉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-07"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-07 21:59:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3517089_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我是把它当作《人间词话》的扩充读本来看的，因为这本书不仅有对《人间词话》的解读，还把作者评论过的词句的原文都附上了，可以算作是换个切入点去读词，优美的其实还是词作本身。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3517089_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3517089_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
