          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wintry_kay/" class=" " title="[已注销]">[已注销]</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="16427044">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">一般的文學評論者或考據專家，往往把文字當解剖學，
拿著一把尖銳的手術刀密密解剖，終於把活的變成死的，
或許看見了雞肉紋理，卻看不到靈魂。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-01-28 17:23</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
